{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"article":{"authorCode":"F3279E8B0F","authorName":"王茂达","classify":"生活类","content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 孤独，我似乎会永远与你为邻。我身边除了你，貌似并不能找到真心陪伴的人。</span><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 孤独，是你培养出我习惯性撒谎等各种不经思考说出的话，说出后又不以为然的继续编下去。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 孤独，是你让我老是装作一副早已习惯的样子，对于身边人的热情推荐横扫门雪。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; ……</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; “朋友”，“兄弟”，你们这两个词为何一直在折磨着我，我的神经，我的思想，我的心情，我的人生。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 我对你们这俩字如此敏感，以致于在交友的过程中遇到小事情就不高兴很久，很久。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 我已记不起小时候和他们一起跑过的操场，一起玩过的老鹰捉小鸡，一起下过的大富翁，一起爬过的山，一起踢过的球，一起打过的乒乓，一起度过的快乐回忆。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 为什么一个高中就让我变得如此窝囊，一个大学让我继续窝囊？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 为什么一个班级就让我变得那么废柴，一个大学让我继续无能？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;难道成熟就是装作一副对什么都早已习惯的样子，把任何感情都埋在自己心里，<span style=\"font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\">alone but pretend not to be lonely?</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 我为什么要在大学同学和辅导员面前装作有女朋友的样子？不经女生同意就把我们的合照给他们看说这是我女票，在一起很久了？</span><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 我为什么要在某某同学面前装作很了解她想接触的某某男生的样子？其实我和那男生的关系并没有我描述的那么熟，那么好？</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 我为什么要装作失恋的样子来引起他们的兴趣却是然并卵？</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 我为什么要搬起石头砸自己的脚？</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 我为什么那么想得到一个朋友？</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nb